you know, certain things about the amolus and all of this.

269
00:26:12,000 --> 00:26:14,000
Some of them was very nice.

270
00:26:14,000 --> 00:26:15,000
Okay.

271
00:26:15,000 --> 00:26:17,000
Okay.

272
00:26:17,000 --> 00:26:27,000
