oh, but days you had ever heard of your life as seeing, you know, how they were just being people down to the ground.

275
00:26:49,000 --> 00:26:58,000
And one of the ladies covered, Shiraz, by the, the keepin' from killing them, though they probably would have killed them.

276
00:26:58,000 --> 00:27:02,000
