00:29:44,000 --> 00:29:50,000
But I wonder what happened to all these people who got beaten up and injured.

321
00:29:50,000 --> 00:29:55,000
You know, you hear about the, they had happened to what happened to the man who was injured.

322
00:29:55,000 --> 00:29:58,000
