00:29:58,000 --> 00:30:07,000
Well, Alka, their injuries was, you know, they still, we still work with the movement.

324
00:30:07,000 --> 00:30:18,000
And worked in Baker County still until we got people registered voting.

325
00:30:18,000 --> 00:30:21,000
Thanks, got a LeComma.

