Oh, yes.

342
00:31:33,000 --> 00:31:37,000
It really gave us the right to speak.

343
00:31:37,000 --> 00:31:41,000
A lot of things, you used to couldn't help a white person.

344
00:31:41,000 --> 00:31:43,000
Say it's something to you.

345
00:31:43,000 --> 00:31:48,000
You weren't allowed maybe to say what you thought.

346
00:31:48,000 --> 00:31:57,000
But now we speak freely, whether, you know, we speak freely and say things that we want to say, you know,

347
00:31:57,000 --> 00:32:00,000
where we used to couldn't respond to them.

348
00:32:00,000 --> 00:32:02,000
And you used to say anything to the white man.

