00:32:02,000 --> 00:32:07,000
You know, knock your down, hit you or kick you or do anything.

350
00:32:07,000 --> 00:32:10,000
But now you have your speech on my speech.

351
00:32:10,000 --> 00:32:12,000
That's one thing we have.

352
00:32:12,000 --> 00:32:17,000
Freedom of speech and we really use it when it's necessary to speak our opinion.

353
00:32:17,000 --> 00:32:18,000
Right.

354
00:32:18,000 --> 00:32:19,000
And the movement helped.

355
00:32:19,000 --> 00:32:20,000
It helped a lot.

